    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Set also <code>android:gravity</code> parameter in <code>TextView</code> to <code>center</code>.</p>\n\n<p>For testing the effects of different layout parameters I recommend to use different background color for every element, so you can see how your layout changes with parameters like gravity, layout_gravity or others.</p>\n"
