    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use the following:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;LinearLayout\n    android:layout_width=\"wrap_content\"\n    android:layout_height=\"wrap_content\"\n    android:id=\"@+id/showdescriptioncontenttitle\"\n    android:paddingTop=\"10dp\"\n    android:paddingBottom=\"10dp\"&gt;\n\n &lt;TextView\n        android:id=\"@+id/textview1\"\n        android:layout_width=\"fill_parent\"\n        android:layout_height=\"wrap_content\"\n        android:gravity=\"center\"\n        android:text=\"Your text\"\n        android:typeface=\"serif\" /&gt;\n&lt;/LinearLayout&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The layout needs to be relative for the \"center\" property to be used.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 6099602,
      "reputation" : 261,
      "user_id" : 4759063,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-fnbEOjL4Ykg/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAABYA/tJu0iEm1HLk/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "sakshi",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/4759063/sakshi"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 26,
    "last_activity_date" : 1428559653,
    "creation_date" : 1428559653,
    "answer_id" : 29530981,
    "question_id" : 7326155,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>use this way in xml </p>\n\n<pre><code>   &lt;TextView\n        android:id=\"@+id/myText\"\n        android:layout_width=\"match_parent\"\n        android:layout_height=\"wrap_content\"\n        android:text=\"Time is precious, so love now.\"\n        android:gravity=\"center\"\n        android:textSize=\"30dp\"\n        android:textColor=\"#fff\"\n        /&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 5654025,
      "reputation" : 553,
      "user_id" : 4473737,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/b4PSz.jpg?s=256",
