    "creation_date" : 1447321665,
    "answer_id" : 33668496,
    "question_id" : 7326155,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Adding <code>android:gravity=\"center\"</code> in your TextView will do the trick (be the parent layout is <code>Relative/Linear</code>)! </p>\n\n<p>Also, you should avoid using dp for font size. Use sp instead.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
