    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>android:layout_gravity=\"center\"\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>android:gravity=\"center\"\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>both works for me.</p>\n"
