    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want to change the alignment from the mainActivity.java file, then use the gravity. For example:</p>\n<pre><code>chatMsg.setGravity(Gravity.RIGHT);\n</code></pre>\n<p>chatMsg is my textView. I wanted the text to be right aligned and this code worked well.</p>\n"
